# NEXT Brand Identity

Brand: **NEXT** (Next Plc, est. 1982)
Guidelines source: https://www.nextguidelines.co.uk
Contact: creative@next.co.uk
Last updated: 14.10.24

---

## Logotype

- The NEXT logotype is uppercase, custom-drawn (not typed in a font).
- Logo font file: `NextLogoFontFinal.ttf` (Drive: BrandIdentity/Fonts/Next Display Fonts).
- Available in **black on white** and **white on black**.
- Only approved rotation: **90 degrees clockwise** (retail/carrier bags only; rarely digital).
- Clear-space padding must always surround the logotype.
- Never stretch, distort, recolour, add effects, or place on busy backgrounds.

